Me? Giant? Mom is WAY bigger than
me—like several TIMES bigger! Hope
I grow that big too...and soon!

I have a fool sister and a terrifying
mom back in Jötunheimr.$k$pHuh? A dad? Uhh... I might have one.
I forget, honestly. Not that important!

I snuck into the kitchen and snagged
a huge pile of sweets... Hey, don't go
telling Alfster on me, all right?!

Hey! Take me somewhere fun, why
don't you! I'm sooooo bored! ...Hey!
Are you even listening to me?!

I've been chatting up lots of folks
around here. Everyone's from some
weird place I've never heard of!

Can't believe I'm being treated like
just another foot soldier even in
$Nf's crew...$k$pHuh? Oh, right. Here.

That's right! Expect nothing less
from me! No one's a match for
THIS jötun!

This seems just about right, wouldn't
you say? Don't go having unrealistic
expectations! I'm just one jötun!
What?! I've been cheated!

Hah! Get ready for the new and
improved Dagr! Oh, and thanks.
You're sweet! *wink*

Hey, I'm Dagr, second of the twin
princesses of Jötunheimr. Hope
you're ready for a good time!$k$pThanks for the invite, by the way!

*yawn* Ah... Sorry—I haven't slept
all that much lately. I've just been
enjoying my time here, y'know?$k$pThere are just so many interesting
people to talk to here, so I end up
staying up half the night!$k$pLike some change into dragons or
are secretly other people... It's wild!$k$pThe world—er, worlds, I guess—have
a lot more going on than I expected!$k$pJust listening to everyone, I feel like
I've learned a ton. I might even be
smarter than I already was! *wink*$k$pI guess what I'm trying to say is that
I'm having fun here, and I'm real
glad you summoned me! That's all!$k$pI'm looking forward to being here for
a while still. Hope I can hear more of
your story too while I'm at it!$k$pGive me a shout sometime, will ya?
Don't be a stranger!
